{
  "stem": "740.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And interesting enough, even that my mother was a Bolshevik, she still had a kosher household, which I could, could never understand.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The two things really don't go together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But I-- listen, I never tried to understand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And there were moments of peace in the house, especially on Friday night, which was very nice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I don't know much about my mother's family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The only one I really knew was my mother, who died very early.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "In my father's family, I know more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They were, for 10 generations, in Germany, coming originally out of the province of Poznan, where all the Poznans come from.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The migration went about 1653, around that time, toward France, Holland, Austria, and Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "My father's family went to Silesia, which the city is today is a Polish name, Breslau.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And in Breslau, they were calling themselves Pozener, which means a people from Posen or Poznan.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "At that time, all the Posners-- the original men was a rabbi, as I understand, a teacher.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And they belonged to the district of Posnanski.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Those were the barons in Poland who owned all the district.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And this is where the name Posner comes from.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the whole family stems from, really, Breslau-- Father, with three boys and three girls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, as I understand, my grandfather, who I've never met, had a hardware store, a small hardware store.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The son was supposed to take it over, but unfortunately, passed away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was shot the first day on the, on the front lines in 1914.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- my father went to the front line four years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my uncle never went to the front lines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a technical artist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when the officer inducted him, asked him for his profession, he said, I'm a painter and a technical artist.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
